ENV.MBE.PARAMETERSGETTINGVERSION.PARAMET.name: ENV.MBE.PARAMETERSGETTINGVERSION.PARAMETERS
ENV.MBE.PARAMETERSGETTINGVERSION.PARAMET.simpleValue:
select *
from (
select version, datetime_str, case when regexp_instr(datetime_str, '\d{2}:\d{2}:\d{2}') = 1 then to_date(datetime_str, 'HH24:MI:SS MM/DD/YYYY') else to_date(datetime_str, 'HH24:MI MM/DD/YYYY') end datetime
from (select substr(value,1,instr(value,' Date: ')-1) version, substr(value,instr(value,' Date: ')+7,length(value)-instr(value,' Date: ')-7) datetime_str from nc_directory where key='nc.database.version.history')
order by datetime desc)
where version like '%qubership.be-%'
and rownum = 1
